looked away. The foremost effect of what 



298 . , 

he had heard had been a sort of irritation 
of his modesty. "Of course," said Felix, 
^^I suggest nothing; it would be veiy 
presumptuous in me to advise you. But 
I think there is no doubt about the 
fact." 

Mr. Brand looked hard at the floor for 
